summary.title: Norwegian Legal Manuscript
summary.note: Made up from two separate manuscripts.

origin.p:
Håndskriftet er skrevet i Iceland i perioden c. 1320, s. XIV in and c. 1350-1370.
Fols 1ra-65vb: c. 1320 (Storm 1885 476 and Hægstad 1907 156 ).
Fols 66v-81v: c. 1300-1320 (Seip 1955 228-229 ).
Fols 82r-87v: c. 1350-1370 (: Seip 1955 218, 233 ).
Kålund's dating: The first half of the fourteenth century ( Katalog ).
